<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Design Thinking | DGT</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

    <link href="index.css"  rel="stylesheet" >
    <script src="/search.js"></script>

    <style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: #fafafa;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f0, #fff);
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px 120px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.1);
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -50px;
            right: -50px;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            color: #2c3e50;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .hero h1::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.3);
            animation: lineExpand 0.6s ease-out 0.8s forwards;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #5d6d7e;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s forwards;
        }

        .hero p span {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(10px);
        }

        .content-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: -60px auto 40px;
            padding: 0 40px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .section-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .classic-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .classic-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 0;
            background: #ff7f50;
            transition: height 0.4s ease;
        }

        .classic-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .classic-card:hover::after {
            height: 100%;
        }

        .classic-card h2 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .classic-card h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 40px;
            height: 2px;
            background: #ff7f50;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .classic-card:hover h2::after {
            width: 80px;
        }

        .classic-card p {
            color: #5d6d7e;
            line-height: 1.8;
            position: relative;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: #fff;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.1);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.1);
        }

        .cta-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, 
                transparent, 
                rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.2), 
                transparent
            );
        }

        .cta-wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .cta-section h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -8px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 2px;
            background: #ff7f50;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            background: transparent;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            border-color: #ff7f50;
            background: rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.05);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .cta-button::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 150%;
            height: 150%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0);
            transition: transform 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .cta-button:hover::before {
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
        }

        .classic-footer {
            background: #1a252f;
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 60px;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }

        .footer-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .footer-section h3::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 30px;
            height: 2px;
            background: #ff7f50;
        }

        .footer-section p, .footer-section li {
            color: #a3b1c2;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .footer-section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .footer-section ul li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .footer-section ul li a {
            color: #a3b1c2;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .footer-section ul li a::before {
            content: 'â†’';
            position: absolute;
            left: -10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            color: #ff7f50;
        }

        .footer-section ul li a:hover {
            color: white;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .footer-section ul li a:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
            left: 0;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: #a3b1c2;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #ff7f50;
            border-color: #ff7f50;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            color: #a3b1c2;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes lineExpand {
            from {
                width: 0;
            }
            to {
                width: 60px;
            }
        }

        @keyframes wordFadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(10px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 80px 20px 100px;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            .section-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .footer-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }
            .content-container {
                padding: 0 20px;
                margin-top: -40px;
            }
            .classic-card {
                padding: 30px;
            }
            .cta-section {
                padding: 40px 20px;
            }
            .cta-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Design Thinking</h1>
            <p class="animated-text">Bridging the gap between technology and human experience through innovative design thinking principles. We transform complex challenges into intuitive, impactful solutions that drive real business value.</p>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="section-grid">
            <div class="classic-card" data-aos="fade-up">
